title: Seth Rollins
summary: Colby Daniel Lopez (born May 28, 1986) is an American professional wrestler, wrestling trainer, and actor. He is currently signed to WWE, where he performs on the Raw brand under the ring name Seth Rollins. He is known by the nicknames "The Architect", "The Kingslayer", and "The Visionary". Noted for his energetic slapstick personas, Rollins has long been considered as one of the greatest in-ring performers of his generation.
